466
00:46:53.519 --> 00:46:56.519
First of all, if you add anything in a roster being

467
00:46:56.519 --> 00:46:59.519
the so-called agreed additional hours and standard hours,

468
00:46:59.519 --> 00:47:04.519
should attract leave accrual, but not necessarily the extra payment.

469
00:47:04.519 --> 00:47:07.519
So there's a benefit to the employee and they would get,

470
00:47:07.519 --> 00:47:11.519
