472
00:47:14.519 --> 00:47:18.519
simply because a portion of that roster is so-called additional hours.

473
00:47:18.519 --> 00:47:21.519
So I think there's a good way to balancing out that issue.

474
00:47:21.519 --> 00:47:24.519
I don't claim to, and I'm certainly not a payroll expert,

475
00:47:24.519 --> 00:47:26.519
I don't claim that it would solve all problems,

