492
00:48:18.519 --> 00:48:21.519
and then normally revert back to their normal operational roster.

493
00:48:21.519 --> 00:48:25.519
So the way that the bill is cast is that all of those additional hours

494
00:48:25.519 --> 00:48:29.519
