495
00:48:29.519 --> 00:48:35.519
whereas the post, so there's a double whammy for both employee

496
00:48:35.519 --> 00:48:39.519
and employer in having just the payment for the extra hours

497
00:48:39.519 --> 00:48:42.519
and no leave for the employee.

498
00:48:42.519 --> 00:48:47.519
It's quite common to have rosters shift around in terms of their variability.

499
00:48:47.519 --> 00:48:50.519
Most rosters, I have to say, most rosters are pretty standard.

500
00:48:50.519 --> 00:48:53.519
